<div id="post-4" class="post-4 page type-page status-publish hentry">
<h1 class="entry-title">
<a href="http://www.nurturingtruth.com/" title="Permalink to Home" rel="bookmark">Home</a>
</h1>
<div class="entry-content">
<p><strong>Hello!</strong></p>
<p><img class="alignright wp-image-52 size-medium" src="http://www.nurturingtruth.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/DSC_1401-300x199.jpg" alt="DSC_1401" width="300" height="199"/></p>
<p>My name is Steven Summerstone. I am a writer, musician, and therapist currently living in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam. I have also been a teacher for six years.<br/>
This site is a staging ground for you and I to work together in therapy sessions.</p>
<p>It&#8217;s also a place where I have posted essays, books, blog entries, videos, and music that represent different stages in my evolving consciousness. Consider these works similar to the timeline diagram of human evolution you&#8217;ve likely seen: a small ape-like creature on one end and an upright, modern-day human on the other end. The older the work, the closer I was to that frail, wounded, and completely terrified creature that emerged from my parents&#8217; home not so long ago. The more recent the work, the more upright it stands and walks. By no means am I fully healed or enlightened but I am striving every day to become more real.</p>
<p>Consider us fellow travelers on the path to truth.</p>
</div>
</div><!-- #post-## -->
</div>
